# List of countries by net goods exports



This is a **list of countries by net goods exports**, also known as **balance of trade**, which is the difference between the monetary value of a nation's exports and imports over a certain time period. The list includes sovereign states and self-governing dependent territories based upon the ISO standard ISO 3166-1. Countries with positive balance of trade have a trade surplus, countries with negative net exports have a trade deficit.
